{
  "stem": "19502.3",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I also worked as a-- worked in a restaurant, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My husband.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That where I met my husband's father.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's a-- it was a-- it wasn't a easy life, let me tell you.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was all by myself, and I had to-- had to-- you know, I used to come home and help out my sister-in-law, and so on.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So it wasn't a very easy life, believe me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then in the middle she-- she had a brother, and he was [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She says, do me a favor.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Go and find my brother.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So-- so I go to [NON-ENGLISH], and down there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Six weeks, I was on the trains, winter time, to find her brother.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "While I was going to go to look for him there, he was there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was-- and you couldn't-- those days, was no such a thing as a ticket.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You just rode the trains, you know, hanging on, with outside.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Look, I had a very, very hard-- it wasn't-- wasn't easy, even though I was liberated.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But you know, when I was liberated, I was afraid for a long time.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "When somebody knocked on the door, I used to go under the bed.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "For a while, I couldn't sleep on a bed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I was embarrassed, you know, when I came in.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So I used to go to bed and then at night I'm going go and lay on the floor.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because I wasn't used to it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I- it-- I was hurting to sleep in a bed, you see.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So there where I used to go, go on the floor.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when somebody came in and-- oh, took me a long time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I always looked over the shoulders.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was very, very afraid.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was frightened, you know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But, of course, I didn't cry.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
